  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You are adept at using your armor to cover your most vulnerable areas.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Base attack bonus +11 or fighter level 8th, armor training class feature, proficiency with medium or heavy armor.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When you are hit by a confirmed critical hit or a sneak attack, there is a 25% chance that the critical hit or sneak attack is negated and damage is instead rolled normally.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>This chance stacks with the light fortification and moderate fortification armor special abilities.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>If you fail to negate a critical hit against you, you can spend 5 stamina points to cause the attack to deal half damage. (See page 17.)",
